{"id":88432,"date":"2018-10-09T15:54:14","date_gmt":"2018-10-09T15:54:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/?p=88432"},"modified":"2019-02-06T08:54:57","modified_gmt":"2019-02-06T08:54:57","slug":"financial-commission-participated-in-2018-trading-show-new-york","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/2018\/10\/09\/financial-commission-participated-in-2018-trading-show-new-york\/","title":{"rendered":"Financial Commission Participated in 2018 Trading Show New York","gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"text"}]},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">October 9th, \u00a02018, The Financial Commission, a leading independent member-driven external dispute resolution (EDR) organization for international online brokerages that participate in global foreign exchange (forex), derivatives, and CFD markets is pleased to announce its recent successful participation at the Trading Show New York, which took place at the Hilton Midtown on September 26th, 2018.<\/p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2.jpg\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-88433 size-400\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-400x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-400x300.jpg 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-830x623.jpg 830w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-230x173.jpg 230w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-350x263.jpg 350w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-480x360.jpg 480w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%; padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY5.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-88469 size-400\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY5-400x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY5-400x300.jpg 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY5-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY5-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY5-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY5-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY5-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY5-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY5-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The event brought together over 300 industry professionals from the blockchain, cryptocurrency, automated trading and advanced analytics fields. Numerous keynote speakers from the digital trading and investment community provided insights into the latest industry trends, challenges, and solutions.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our representatives met in person with event delegates to discuss new blockchain and cryptocurrency technologies, as well as regulatory efforts in the space. Likewise, during the event, we met with representatives of <a href=\"https:\/\/tradefora.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tradefora<\/a>, a new provider of trading cost and execution analytics for FX, CFD and cryptocurrency traders. Given the Commission\u2019s continuing goal of increasing transparency for all market participants, our lengthy discussion focused on new approaches to helping traders understand the true costs associated with trading the markets.<\/p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY3.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-88451 size-400\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY3-400x533.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY3-400x533.jpg 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY3-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY3-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY3-200x267.jpg 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY3-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY3-800x1067.jpg 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY3.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%; padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-88460 size-400\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY4-400x533.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY4-400x533.jpg 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY4-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY4-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY4-200x267.jpg 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY4-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY4-800x1067.jpg 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/NY4.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Commenting about the event participation, Financial Commission Chairman, Peter Tatarnikov said, \u201cDigital commodity trading and blockchain technology are becoming an ever important topic for the Financial Commission. For this reason, our participation in the Trading Show New York was important to help us to continue formulating our strategy on self-regulatory efforts for digital commodities and financial firms that transact on the blockchain. We look forward to future events both in New York and elsewhere to interact with our professional and regulatory counterparts on improving conditions in these growing new markets.\u201d<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To learn more about how the Financial Commission provides digital commodity traders and cryptocurrency firms with an effective dispute resolution channel visit<a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\"> FinancialCommission.org<\/a> or contact us to learn more about our services.<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>October 9th, \u00a02018, The Financial Commission, a leading independent member-driven external dispute resolution (EDR) organization for international online brokerages that participate in global foreign exchange (forex), derivatives, and CFD markets is pleased to announce its recent successful participation at the Trading Show New York, which took place at the Hilton Midtown on September 26th, 2018. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"author":13,"featured_media":88433,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[14,12,16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-88432","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-commission-news","category-company-news-news-events","category-press-releases-news-events"],"acf":[],"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"link","format":"url"}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/88432","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/13"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=88432"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/88432\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/88433"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=88432"}],"wp: